SubjectLease with Bell Technical Solutions Inc. ** NCC **
PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to grant one option of three years, commencing on June 1st, 2018, to extend an existing lease with BELL TECHNICAL SOLUTIONS INC. to occupy a property located at 1740 WOODROFFE AVENUE in Ottawa, known as building 101.
